15 account, surety bond, interest rate lock or swap arrangement, hedging arrangement,
16 liquidity or credit support arrangement, or other financial arrangement entered into
17 in connection with securitized bonds;
18 (2) "Assignee" means a legally recognized entity to which an electric utility assigns,
