8 Section 6. Whereas the cost of electric energy is rising and the health and safety
9 of the citizens of the Commonwealth depends on lower cost energy through increased
10 electric generation, an emergency is declared to exist, and this Act takes effect upon its
11 passage and approval by the Governor or upon its otherwise becoming a law.
